Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.72,0:00:02.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dragon Slayer's Secret Art!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.25,0:00:06.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Has she already mastered them both?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.36,0:00:08.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.30,0:00:09.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.44,0:00:11.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wendy knows the Secret Art?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.50,0:00:13.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.00,0:00:14.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She's as good as won.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.30,0:00:16.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.85,0:00:18.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A magic wind barrier?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.26,0:00:20.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You've sealed us inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.49,0:00:23.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Light Burst: Sky Drill!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.96,0:00:39.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheria!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.10,0:00:41.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.70,0:00:41.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.72,0:00:48.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't mastered Milky Way yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.56,0:00:51.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...so this was my full force.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.53,0:00:54.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I used all my magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.32,0:00:57.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.55,0:01:03.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You were wonderful, Wendy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.32,0:01:08.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I went overboard...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.65,0:01:09.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But this way...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.76,0:01:12.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheria's down!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.60,0:01:16.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The winner, from Fairy Tail A...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.17,0:01:18.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry! Wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.15,0:01:20.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just getting started!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.27,0:01:27.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're impressive, Wendy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.55,0:01:31.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay? Want to give up?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.47,0:03:08.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye, sir! The Grand Magic Games \Nare really picking up steam!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.28,0:03:10.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu's Fairy Tail Team A
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.69,0:03:14.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,was in eighth place for the qualifier, \Nbarely making it to the real games,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.90,0:03:16.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and then they got creamed the first day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.97,0:03:19.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But even so, through Natsu's good showing,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.50,0:03:22.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,their points rose little by little!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.22,0:03:25.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But with Raven Tail's pesky obstructions...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.84,0:03:28.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...B Team got off to a rocky start, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.75,0:03:32.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And we can't forget Sabertooth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.20,0:03:36.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Currently, they're known as \Nthe strongest guild in Fiore.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.88,0:03:40.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They've got two Dragon Slayers \Nin their ranks, Sting and Rogue.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.99,0:03:43.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Their abilities are top-notch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.17,0:03:46.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A lot happened with Yukino, \Na Celestial Spirit Wizard,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.83,0:03:48.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but they're formidable enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.83,0:03:53.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of "a lot happened", \NRaven Tail's Alexei
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.55,0:03:56.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,was revealed to be guild master Ivan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.00,0:04:00.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ivan is our master Makarov's son.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.03,0:04:02.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, he's Laxus's son.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.83,0:04:08.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And Gajeel had been working as a double \Nagent in order to investigate Raven Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.26,0:04:11.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,At last, the showdown between \Nfather and son guilds was over.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.23,0:04:16.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Continuing with the battle \Npart, Wendy was up next
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.65,0:04:18.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,against Cheria from Lamia Scale!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.84,0:04:20.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She's Sherry's cousin!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.89,0:04:28.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear Lamia Scale and Blue Pegasus once \Nallied with Fairy Tail to battle Oracion Seis?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.80,0:04:30.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.44,0:04:34.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A magical celebration with a mix \Nof old faces and new guilds,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.85,0:04:36.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,that's the Grand Magic Games!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.46,0:04:39.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, everyone! Thank \Nyou for your patience!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.83,0:04:42.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's continue with the \NWendy vs. Cheria battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.84,0:04:46.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hooray! Hooray! Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.63,0:05:01.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you're not going to give up?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.83,0:05:06.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wendy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.00,0:05:07.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She can barely stand!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.33,0:05:09.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wendy...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.56,0:05:11.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is an incredible fight...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.93,0:05:20.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Small Fist!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.75,0:05:27.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If that Cheria girl
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.95,0:05:30.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,has some connection to Zeref...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.22,0:05:35.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...Wendy is in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.12,0:05:36.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.58,0:05:37.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? This guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.22,0:05:39.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,From Fairy Tail...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.94,0:05:42.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Should I stop this? Or wait and see?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.81,0:05:46.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wendy...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.59,0:05:50.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.55,0:05:54.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Seven years ago, I infiltrated Fairy Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.27,0:06:00.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,To some extent, I'm acquainted with \Ninside information on Fairy Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.38,0:06:02.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mystogan...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.95,0:06:05.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not supposed to exist in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.92,0:06:19.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind fighting,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.42,0:06:23.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but I've got no love for one-sided \Nviolence where the outcome is clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.44,0:06:32.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Council... At a time like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.17,0:06:36.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, you can always surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.86,0:06:39.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.29,0:06:50.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that I'm standing here
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.77,0:06:54.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,means that I'm prepared \Nto fight for my guild!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.33,0:06:56.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need your pity.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.22,0:06:59.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Until I fall and can't move anymore,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.88,0:07:01.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,come at me with everything you've got!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.85,0:07:02.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.04,0:07:07.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wendy...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.96,0:07:18.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.28,0:07:19.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's only common courtesy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.12,0:07:21.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.12,0:07:24.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, now it's my turn \Nto break out a big move!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.05,0:07:28.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make it easy on you and \Nend this with one strike.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.97,0:07:35.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,God Slayer's Secret Art!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.51,0:07:36.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheria, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.82,0:07:37.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.28,0:07:41.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool! Do you mean to kill your opponent?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.45,0:07:48.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm answering the full strength of \Nyour feelings with my full strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.44,0:07:50.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what love is!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.12,0:07:57.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What is that magic?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.70,0:07:59.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.91,0:08:02.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heaven's Gathering Clouds!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.26,0:08:17.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She dodged it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.69,0:08:19.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No... It missed her!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.14,0:08:23.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems Cheria can heal \Nherself with her magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.57,0:08:25.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but it only works on wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.66,0:08:28.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like she can't \Nrecharge herself with energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.40,0:08:29.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.77,0:08:33.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wendy's the opposite. She can't \Nheal herself with her magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.66,0:08:35.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but she can restore another \Nperson's strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.80,0:08:37.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.29,0:08:39.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.66,0:08:42.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...she revived her opponent's \Nphysical strength?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.25,0:08:49.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And because of that, Cheria's \Nmagic gained too much force...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.39,0:08:55.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wendy made her miss...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.18,0:08:58.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...by increasing her strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.04,0:09:04.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What strategy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.85,0:09:06.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.44,0:09:07.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Crushing Fang...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.67,0:09:10.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...of the Sky Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.78,0:09:14.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's great, Wendy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.17,0:09:31.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is an incredible turn of events!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.31,0:09:33.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Neither side is giving any ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.70,0:09:38.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a clash of little fists! Is this \Ntenacity for the sake of their guilds?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.33,0:09:42.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stop this...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.06,0:09:49.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Though their fists are small,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.16,0:09:52.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,their passion is vast...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.77,0:10:04.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Neither of you lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.73,0:10:08.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wendy...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.54,0:10:25.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And so...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.72,0:10:28.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...time has run out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.66,0:10:46.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The match is over and it's a draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.00,0:10:52.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Both teams receive five points!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.40,0:10:53.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.82,0:10:56.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You did great, Wendy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.13,0:10:57.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Both of them were magnificent.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.30,0:10:59.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.75,0:11:02.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheria and Wendy both did very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.16,0:11:03.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We were lucky to get to see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.93,0:11:09.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the best match I've seen yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.51,0:11:15.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though judging them on magic \Nalone, Cheria's level is far higher...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.82,0:11:17.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.80,0:11:18.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.30,0:11:22.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm no good when it comes to battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.00,0:11:26.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but I can use a lot of support magic \Nthat'll be useful to everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.63,0:11:31.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So... So please don't leave me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.96,0:11:33.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The girl from back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.60,0:11:37.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...has grown this much...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.48,0:11:39.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wendy...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.77,0:11:42.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are you crying for?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.85,0:11:52.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did it hurt? I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.27,0:11:54.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine. That's all I hear from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.88,0:12:01.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That was fun, Wendy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.69,0:12:05.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My wounds...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.78,0:12:09.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I enjoyed it too, a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.83,0:12:12.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, let's be friends, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.47,0:12:14.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.24,0:12:16.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, if you want me as a friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.03,0:12:17.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.35,0:12:18.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Answer like friends are supposed to.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.50,0:12:23.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's be friends, Wendy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.35,0:12:26.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, Cheria!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.58,0:12:33.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What a moving ending!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.18,0:12:37.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For this old man, the tournament is over!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.06,0:12:40.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on there. Just the third day is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.12,0:12:44.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.63,0:12:54.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.33,0:12:59.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though the fight's over, that \Nsinister magic is still around?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.26,0:13:03.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then Cheria isn't the source of that magic?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.70,0:13:06.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's from over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.25,0:13:08.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heading towards the exit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.07,0:13:16.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did he notice me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.18,0:13:18.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.67,0:13:28.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, the third day ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.20,0:13:33.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,At this point, Sabertooth is \Nthe top team with 34 points.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.02,0:13:35.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mermaid Heel is in second place.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.33,0:13:37.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lamia Scale is in third,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.42,0:13:39.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,making those the best three.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.75,0:13:42.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Below them, the order goes Fairy Tail B, A,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.99,0:13:45.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and then Blue Pegasus.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.77,0:13:49.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy Tail's showing is unexpected.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.61,0:13:54.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps I need to think a bit-k-kabo...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.82,0:14:00.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The source of that mysterious magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.77,0:14:05.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.07,0:14:07.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I found him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.06,0:14:16.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He came out of nowhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.32,0:14:17.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not going anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.09,0:14:24.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though the person who possesses that \Nmysterious magic is right over there...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.15,0:14:26.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.22,0:14:29.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll put him to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.51,0:14:30.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.00,0:14:34.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, I'm supposed \Nto be a Fairy Tail wizard.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.01,0:14:37.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't lay a hand on a \Nmember of the Council.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.59,0:14:41.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Doranbolt, what's all the commotion about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.53,0:14:42.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.68,0:14:45.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you're not Mystogan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.14,0:14:47.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.40,0:15:10.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll ask once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.29,0:15:12.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.78,0:15:16.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I'm in a hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.17,0:15:18.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, you don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.10,0:15:21.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mystogan isn't in Earthland.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.52,0:15:23.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Mystogan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.52,0:15:25.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.90,0:15:28.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.51,0:15:37.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starvin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.40,0:15:38.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.94,0:15:42.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm trying to bask in the afterglow \Nof that touching ending!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.37,0:15:45.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't help bein' hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.05,0:15:48.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, let's get somethin' to eat, Happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.80,0:15:50.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's incorrigible...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.42,0:15:53.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Me too...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.30,0:15:55.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.26,0:15:56.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeesh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.80,0:15:57.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.20,0:16:01.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We got to see a good match today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.10,0:16:03.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure dinner will be really good tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.40,0:16:06.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.62,0:16:12.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jellal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.84,0:16:40.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so there you are, Mystogan-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.35,0:16:41.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yajima-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.77,0:16:44.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lahar-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.25,0:16:48.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You can understand why Mystogan-kun \Nhides his face, can't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.27,0:16:54.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He was unlucky enough to be born \Nwith the same face as Jellal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.45,0:16:56.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.85,0:16:58.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're saying... He's another person?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.54,0:17:03.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps you know of the world called Edolas?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.08,0:17:05.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I heard about it from \None of my subordinates.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.06,0:17:09.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That world and this one are connected.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.73,0:17:12.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There are people who have the same faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.81,0:17:16.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you're from Edolas?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.51,0:17:18.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.84,0:17:21.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a great match, wasn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.62,0:17:21.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.85,0:17:29.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jellal!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.57,0:17:32.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagura!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.41,0:17:37.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.11,0:17:37.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagura-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.90,0:17:38.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagura-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.62,0:17:48.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagura! Get a hold of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.90,0:17:51.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody call for a medic!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.19,0:17:52.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagura-chan is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.36,0:17:53.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.29,0:17:54.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.46,0:17:59.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jell...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.12,0:18:06.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all right now. I've calmed down.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.14,0:18:09.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But {\i1}he's{\i0} over there...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.08,0:18:11.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.03,0:18:13.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm okay now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.83,0:18:14.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.80,0:18:19.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So they've been hiding him...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.65,0:18:23.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jellal in Fairy Tail...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.00,0:18:27.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, Er-chan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.42,0:18:33.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I appreciate your understanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.79,0:18:34.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.85,0:18:38.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize for not knowing \Nthe circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.52,0:18:42.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,To me, Jellal is an evil being.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.35,0:18:45.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If I run into him, you \Ncan bet I'll report him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.91,0:18:46.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.00,0:18:47.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.79,0:18:51.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I owe you, Yajima-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.45,0:18:53.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just this once.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.49,0:18:56.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of here before you \Ncause Makarov any trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.98,0:18:57.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.45,0:19:01.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I swear I'll be gone by the \Ntime the tournament is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.25,0:19:05.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the real thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.33,0:19:09.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want Yajima-san to lose face here,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.93,0:19:11.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but we won't let {\i1}him{\i0} get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.48,0:19:23.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I lose him?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.24,0:19:28.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That magic was like Zeref's \Nand yet it wasn't his.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.60,0:19:30.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.52,0:19:55.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.38,0:20:01.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...somewhere in Gramps' \Nheart, he had faith in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.80,0:20:04.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you're father and son...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.34,0:20:07.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.81,0:20:13.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting all this time for this day!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.58,0:20:17.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It was all to get Lumen Histoire!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.40,0:20:20.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Lumen Histoire?! Where is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.82,0:20:25.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me, Laxus! You're my son, aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.49,0:20:31.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gramps...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.22,0:20:34.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's Lumen Histoire?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.66,0:20:38.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You heard this from Ivan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.62,0:20:44.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heard about it? All I know \Nis he wanted it badly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.56,0:20:47.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That brat will be the end of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.96,0:20:51.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He called it "Fairy Tail's darkness".
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.42,0:20:59.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.11,0:21:00.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,First Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.35,0:21:04.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lumen Histoire...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.70,0:21:07.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's our guild's light.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.49,0:21:09.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,First Master, you mustn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.61,0:21:11.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.86,0:21:16.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Only the master of this guild \Nhas the right to know about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.93,0:21:20.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Laxus, do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.40,0:21:24.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If it ain't anything weird, then \NI won't bother looking into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.99,0:21:26.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.15,0:21:32.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But where did Ivan get \Nahold of that information?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.54,0:21:34.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The second master...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.73,0:21:37.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It was likely Purehito.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.48,0:21:41.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's possible...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.49,0:21:45.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I never imagined that Purehito \Nwould fall to the dark side.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.17,0:21:48.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And now, as a result of my \Nshallow-brained selection...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.74,0:21:50.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.08,0:21:52.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not your fault, First Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.54,0:21:54.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It is my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.11,0:21:56.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.27,0:22:05.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,First Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.09,0:22:10.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,G-Gramps! What do we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.48,0:22:13.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not crying! Not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.08,0:22:17.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not... crying...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.56,0:22:20.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Laxus!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.10,0:22:22.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on, hold her!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.73,0:22:24.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That hurdle's too high!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.65,0:23:58.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, another battle in bathing suits!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.45,0:23:59.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.56,0:24:03.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just before, I saw a swimsuit that was laid \Nout in the dressing room of another guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.86,0:24:04.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, so?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.39,0:24:06.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It was just the bottoms!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.30,0:24:08.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning a contestant went out there topless!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.63,0:24:10.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh! That's wild!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.87,0:24:13.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not really the reaction \NI was looking for...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.99,0:24:16.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: Naval Battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.51,0:24:17.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of reaction did you expect?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.96,0:24:20.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"Wowie! Are you serious?!" Like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.14,0:24:23.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Or "I'm goin' to the front line!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.52,0:24:24.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is that?
